==病因與診斷==
黃斑部病變通常發生於年長者<!-- <ref name=NEI2015/> -->。基因、抽菸以及過度接觸陽光照射<ref>{{Cite web|title=【黃斑點病變】《陳卓琪眼科醫生》在【東周刊】【東周網】講解【黃斑點病變】|url=http://eyecarehk.org/eyecareaction/eastweekly01-201907/|accessdate=2019-08-10|author=|date=2019-06-13|last=|format=|work=睛明護眼 www.EyeCareHK.org|publisher=|language=zh-HK|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225195756/http://eyecarehk.org/eyecareaction/eastweekly01-201907/|dead-url=no}}</ref>也會有所影響<!-- <ref name=NEI2015/> -->。這是由於[[視網膜|視網膜]][[视网膜黄斑|黃斑]]的損傷所造成<!-- <ref name=NEI2015/> -->。可以完整的[[視力測試|視力測試]]診斷得知<!-- <ref name=NEI2015/> -->。眼科醫生會進行放大瞳孔檢查眼底作初部檢查，醫生亦可能會建議患者接受眼底螢光造影及光學同步眼底掃描作進一步檢查，判斷是哪一種黃斑點病變及病情。<ref>{{Cite web|title=黃斑點病變|url=http://eyecarehk.org/maculardegeneration/|accessdate=2019-08-10|work=睛明護眼 www.EyeCareHK.org|language=zh-HK|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225185156/http://eyecarehk.org/maculardegeneration/|dead-url=no}}</ref>病情依嚴重程度可分為輕度、中度及重度<ref name="NEI2015" />。重度的老年性黃斑部病變可被另外分成乾性與濕性，而90%為乾性老年性黃斑部病變<ref name="NEI2015" /><ref name="Meh2015" />。<!-- 預防與治療 Prevention and treatment -->

預防老年性黃斑部病變的方法包含戒菸、運動及健康的飲食<ref name=NEI2015>{{cite web|title=Facts About Age-Related Macular Degeneration|publisher=National Eye Institute|url=https://nei.nih.gov/health/maculardegen/armd_facts|website=NEI|accessdate=21 December 2015|date=June 2015|archive-date=2015-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222151236/https://nei.nih.gov/health/maculardegen/armd_facts|dead-url=no}}</ref>。補充維生素沒有明顯的預防效果<ref name=Evans2012>{{cite journal |author=Evans JR, Lawrenson JG |title=Antioxidant vitamin and mineral supplements for preventing age-related macular degeneration |journal=Cochrane Database Syst Rev |volume=6 |issue= |pages=CD000253 |year=2012 |pmid=22696317 |doi=10.1002/14651858.CD000253.pub3 |editor1-last=Evans |editor1-first=Jennifer R}}</ref>。一旦視力已經喪失，就無法痊癒或治療恢復<!-- <ref name=NEI2015/> -->。在濕性老年性黃斑部病變的治療方式有眼內注射{{tsl|en|anti-VEGF medication|抗血管內皮增生因子|抗血管內皮增生因子}}，較少見的{{tsl|en|laser coagulation|雷射光凝固治療|雷射光凝固治療}}或[[光動力療法|光動力療法]]都可能減緩病情惡化<ref name=NEI2015/><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.kmuh.org.tw/www/kmcj/data/9708/14.htm|title=老年性黃斑部病變及最新治療|accessdate=2016-10-11|author=吳文權|date=2008-08-01|work=高醫醫訊月刊|publisher=高雄醫學大學附設中和紀念醫院|archive-date=2020-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200527133729/http://www.kmuh.org.tw/www/kmcj/data/9708/14.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。已有老年性黃斑部病變的的患者，補充有益的營養成分可以減緩病情惡化<ref name=Evan2012Already>{{cite journal|last1=Evans|first1=JR|last2=Lawrenson|first2=JG|title=Antioxidant vitamin and mineral supplements for slowing the progression of age-related macular degeneration.|journal=The Cochrane database of systematic reviews|date=14 November 2012|volume=11|pages=CD000254|pmid=23152201}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ntuh.gov.tw/OPH/DocLib10/%E8%80%81%E5%B9%B4%E6%80%A7%E9%BB%83%E6%96%91%E9%83%A8%E7%97%85%E8%AE%8A.aspx|title=老年性黃斑部病變|accessdate=2016-10-11|author=|date=|work=www.ntuh.gov.tw|publisher=臺大醫院眼科部|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161011223555/https://www.ntuh.gov.tw/OPH/DocLib10/%E8%80%81%E5%B9%B4%E6%80%A7%E9%BB%83%E6%96%91%E9%83%A8%E7%97%85%E8%AE%8A.aspx|archive-date=2016-10-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

==流行病學==
在2010年全球有兩千三百萬的人有老年性黃斑部病變<ref name=Vel2014>{{cite journal|last1=Velez-Montoya|first1=R|last2=Oliver|first2=SC|last3=Olson|first3=JL|last4=Fine|first4=SL|last5=Quiroz-Mercado|first5=H|last6=Mandava|first6=N|title=Current knowledge and trends in age-related macular degeneration: genetics, epidemiology, and prevention.|journal=Retina (Philadelphia, Pa.)|date=March 2014|volume=34|issue=3|pages=423-41|pmid=24285245}}</ref>。在2013年，中度到重度的病患有一千三百四十萬人，且這是在繼[[白內障|白內障]]、[[早產|早產]]及[[青光眼|青光眼]]後造成失明的第四常見的主要因素<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Global Burden of Disease Study 2013|first1=Collaborators|title=Global, regional, and national incidence, prevalence, and years lived with disability for 301 acute and chronic diseases and injuries in 188 countries, 1990-2013: a systematic analysis for the Global Burden of Disease Study 2013.|journal=Lancet (London, England)|date=22 August 2015|volume=386|issue=9995|pages=743-800|pmid=26063472}}</ref>。超過五十歲的人較容易出現老年性黃斑部病變，在美國，老年性黃斑部病變為造成此年齡族群失去視力的主要因素<ref name=NEI2015/><ref name=Meh2015>{{cite journal|last1=Mehta|first1=S|title=Age-Related Macular Degeneration.|journal=Primary care|date=September 2015|volume=42|issue=3|pages=377-91|pmid=26319344}}</ref>。年齡50到60歲的人，約有0.4%有此疾病；而60到70歲的人約有0.7%有；年齡70到80歲的人約2.3%有，在超過80歲的人中則有將近12%的人有老年性黃斑部病變<ref name=Meh2015/>。

